{"tid":1704733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢五個月 割咗好多朋友","createTime":"2019-11-10T20:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T22:19:24.000Z","uid":144862,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e033e00cf714318f788091406f61a0ebb6165c","tid":1704733,"uid":144862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T20:04:34.000Z","msg":"係呢五個月 我同好多港豬割蓆<br />\n淨返嘅真朋友 十隻手指數得曬 全部都係前線勇武 <br />\n雖然講就話唔會同港豬割 <br />\n但我見到好多其他區嘅前線手足被捕嘅時候<br />\n再打開ig睇下 好多人食生日飯 飲酒 去OP<br />\n究竟班不理世事嘅港豬 幾時先識醒下？<br />\n就係因為班偽黃港豬乜都唔做 而家先會變成咁<br />\n對唔住開呢個post 係想講出我呢五個月嘅心底話 發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆，不分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d99e6d623b4913febf9f8fccfcc89caaa4a462de","tid":1704733,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"提返大家 全民<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攝衫</span></span>防狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704278\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7af11b6dcf895249723f58412f083751a7c2cb29","tid":1704733,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T20:05:10.000Z","msg":"u are not alone bro"},{"pid":"2eaf22d6556b4f82da260e43da2fc732d3606f0f","tid":1704733,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T20:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afcd9b5f13e45d6efd02cba8350797b6f99dd01","tid":1704733,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T21:21:38.000Z","msg":"你都好啦，我得返1隻手既數目，上前線既仲係更少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683bed5496629559a1fd1ad9a0884ac3d4538362","tid":1704733,"uid":50274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T22:02:20.000Z","msg":"我冇上過前線 你話我怕事都好<br />\n但如果我身邊朋友有咩事 包佢食飯上我屋企避難 做支持佢既朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a537afc22bf73c8832f3f90a1913370e64a45f","tid":1704733,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T22:12:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a7a63002030c27185fc51044e604b93fd345fb4","tid":1704733,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T22:19:24.000Z","msg":"True , fb見到啲吃喝玩樂即unfriend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}